title: Brazilian Girls ~ This is
description:
Well I was totally taken on my first Google search for "Brazilian Girls"....my what a selection

anyway what I have to offer here is in remiss of Verve-Universal Music&#039;s total lack of promotion of one of the todays greatest New York bands. Damn they have toured Ibiza, Europe, & most of the world, but not ever been promoted in the southern isles!!!

So I&#039;ve upped this compilation as an "up yours Universal!" to show the world what an amazing band Brazilian Girls are.

I&#039;ve included scanned cover art & other pics....nothing needs censorship

check it out....if you like the Eurythmics, B52&#039;s, Francoise Hardy, Malcolm McLaren...then this might have some appeal to you

this is one of my all-time favorite bands now

find a store who has their music, plus object to Polygram-Universal for their lack of support

cheers Gazza
